title: T206 Crandall (cap) and Conroy (w/ bat) Dupes
author: jlynch1960

posts.post_title: T206 Crandall (cap) and Conroy (w/ bat) Dupes
posts.post_content:
Sold.

The dangers of buying on Ebay away from the T206 database.  Ended up with these two duplicates.  Both backs are Piedmont 350-460, with some minor paper loss on the Crandall.

I paid $17.85 for the Crandall and $36 for the Conroy.  Would be willing to sell in the same ballpark, shipping included.
